OL,3,CWorld Cup demand boosts pubs but
OL,4,Crestaurant and bar sales stumble
OL,6,FEngland and Scotland World Cup matches
OL,7,Fhelped drive stronger sales across
OL,8,FBritish pubs last month while
OL,9,Frestaurants and bars suffered a weaker
OL,10,Fmonth, according to new figures.
OL,12,FThe latest monthly NIQ RSM hospitality
OL,13,Fbusiness tracker showed that pubs were
OL,14,Fthe standout performer across the
OL,15,Fhospitality sector during the month
OL,16,Fdue to the boost from football fans.
OL,18,FExperts have said they expect
OL,19,FEngland's progress to the semi-finals
OL,20,Fwill have also driven a "stronger"
OL,21,Fperformance this month.
