OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784767668
OL,3,CWorld Cup demand boosts pubs but
OL,4,Crestaurant and bar sales stumble
OL,6,FLike-for-like sales grew by 1.9%
OL,7,Facross British pubs last month,
OL,8,Fmarking the strongest monthly
OL,9,Fperformance this year.
OL,11,FPubs also heavily benefited from long
OL,12,Fperiods of warm weather across parts
OL,13,Fof the country, as England saw the
OL,14,Fhottest June on record, according to
OL,15,Fthe Met Office.
OL,17,FBut other areas of the hospitality
OL,18,Fsector found it harder to attract
OL,19,Ffootfall as many consumers remained
OL,20,Fcautious about their finances.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
