PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784767668
OL,3,CWorld Cup demand boosts pubs but
OL,4,Crestaurant and bar sales stumble
OL,6,FSales at restaurants slipped by 0.7%
OL,7,Fyear-on-year, marking the second-worst
OL,8,Fmonth so far in 2026.
OL,10,FBars suffered another significant
OL,11,Fslump in sales, with a drop of 5.8%
OL,12,Ffor the month.
OL,14,FSales across all parts of the
OL,15,Fhospitality sector were marginally
OL,16,Fhigher, at 0.2%, driven by the strong
OL,17,Fshowing from pubs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
