FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1784767668
OL,3,CWorld Cup demand boosts pubs but
OL,4,Crestaurant and bar sales stumble
OL,6,FSaxon Moseley, head of leisure and
OL,7,Fhospitality at RSM UK, said: "Good
OL,8,Fnews for one segment of the
OL,9,Fhospitality market invariably means
OL,10,Fothers coming under pressure, with
OL,11,Frestaurants, bars and on-the-go
OL,12,Foutlets all losing ground in June.
OL,14,F"As we look ahead to the second half
OL,15,Fof the year, operators will be hoping
OL,16,Fthat Andy Burnham delivers on his
OL,17,Fpromise to reform business rates and
OL,18,Fput more cash in consumers' pockets."
